Installation
------------

To install, just run:

 ./install.sh

as root. You can set DESTDIR to change the installation target:

 DESTDIR=/my/custom/installation/target ./install.sh

Uninstallation
--------------
To remove, you can just:

 rm /usr/bin/xdgmenumaker
 rm /usr/share/desktop-directories/xdgmenumaker*
